snippet.title: EVILVEVIL Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
EvilvEvil is a co-op first-person vampire shooter with a player-directed, continuously updated storyline. Its cast of characters will bring ultracool vampires with a heavy dose of attitude and other monstrosities. Visit the website at https://www.evilvevil.com to sign-up and stay informed about the game.

Developed by Toadman Interactive, an EG7 company.
